'''Mukova''' (Port of Entry kuEnglish) inzvimbo inopindwa nayo nevanhu pamwe nenhumbi. Takatarisana ne[[hushangazhi]], mukova inzvimbo yakatenderwa pamutemo wenyika kuti ipindwe nayo nevanhu kana nhumbi. Pamitemo yenyika pamukova iyoyi ndipo chete panotenderwa kupinda kwevanhu nenhumbi 


==Mhando dzeMukova==

Mukova unogona kuva pamuganhu wenyika kana kuva mukati menyika.

*Mukova iri pamiganhu yenyika yeZimbabwe inosanganisira: Beitbridge; Plumtree; Kazungula; Kariba; Nyamapanda; Forbes zvichingodaro. Mukova iyi inobatanidza Zimbabwe nenyika dzakaipoteredza dzinoti: Mozambique; South Africa; Botswana; Namibia; neZambia.
